Before deploying

Make sure these are true:

✅ The project runs locally without errors.
✅ API keys are stored in environment variables, not in source code.
✅ React uses VITE_API_URL instead of http://localhost:8080.
✅ Backend CORS includes both http://localhost:5173 and your Vercel domain.
✅ Your code is pushed to GitHub.

If you follow these steps, you'll have a live application that you can share in your resume, LinkedIn, and portfolio.